### While Loops

```kotlin

    val shoppingList = mutableListOf("Car", "Mosca", "As3s", "As3s", "As3s", "As3s")


    var counter = 0
    while (counter < shoppingList.size) {
        println(shoppingList[counter])
        counter++
    }

````

### For Loops

```kotlin

   val shoppingList = mutableListOf("Car", "Mosca", "As3s", "As3s", "As3s", "As3s")

// Print Values in Array   

    for(shoppingItem in shoppingList){
        println(shoppingItem)
    }

//  Print Range 

   for(i in 1..100){
        println(i)
    }

````
